	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The TGROM picture shows four chips (row 1: PRG ROM, CHR RAM, CIC; row 2: MMC3), but no PRG RAM.
<br />
<br />RAM chips do not need to be programmed, but the board may need to be rewired slightly to accept them.

		

